data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Cape Coral! With 1,580 square feet of well-designed living space, this property is ready to become your place to relax. Step inside, and you'll immediately notice the open and inviting layout, filled with natural light that enhances the welcoming atmosphere. The adjoining kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and plenty of cabinets for storage. The primary bedroom is a serene retreat with an ensuite bathroom, offering convenience and privacy. Two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family, guests, or even a home office. The second bathroom is conveniently located and features modern fixtures and finishes. One of the standout features of this property is the paved backyard oasis. Step outside to discover a spacious outdoor area, complete with a gazebo, perfect for alfresco dining or simply enjoying the Florida sunshine. And if you're looking to beat the heat, the above-ground pool is an ideal spot for cooling off and making lasting memories with family and friends. This home has CITY WATER AND SEWER as well as a NEWER ROOF, AC & Water heater!
